Banned from [[span style="color:blue;"]]@playmahjong[[/span]] for "unacceptable offsite behaviour" are we taking the piss. What did I do that was unacceptable? I don't use the chats on site specifically so I don't get into shit for this. Literally just played the game before bed most nights before going to sleep.

But now I'm banned. I made one tweet. One fucking tweet. I didn't name anyone. I didn't even name the fucking site I play on. But some sad little cunt has taken the time out of their day to find my account and report me for it anyway. Get a fucking grip.

I won't be appealing.
