Before I go offline to prepare for the tournament, I want to give a massive thank you to [[span style="color:blue;"]]@mecandoit[[/span]] for the help with this project. I couldn't have done this without you and I will not forget your help when I win this shit.

To everyone else, I won't be posting until the tournament now. See you all there.
